{"tid":728770,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"Huawei 智能手錶設計申專利！可收納藍牙耳機？","createTime":"2018-07-04T04:10:36.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-06T06:10:59.000Z","uid":52215,"like":5,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"d0f4205aeb5af59d82362d611103221288f013e4","tid":728770,"uid":52215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-04T04:10:36.000Z","msg":"我都曾經諗過，咁就真係方便用手錶打電話<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/04/121003_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F04%2F121003_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=69288223&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/04/121005_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F04%2F121005_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=74caeb26&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\nHuawei 品牌在歐洲不少地區名聲響噹噹，除了是因為市場策略得宜，其出色產品設計、實用功能，以至用戶評價，亦應記一功。雖說近年 Huawei 好像僅專注於手機產品業務或是網絡發展，而忽略了其他產品線，不過事實是 Huawei 正為下代智能手錶努力着手，並已向世界知識產權組織提交了一項新的設計專利，打算推出一款可收納耳機的智能手錶。<br />\n<br />\n【相關文章】Huawei 摺屏電競 5G 手機 最快 2018 年底搶閘亮相<br />\n<br />\n據 LetsGoDigital 報道，世界智識產權組織近日批准了一項由 Huawei 提交的設計專利文件。這項專利描述，Huawei 這款智能手錶專利設計，最注目的之處是錶帶部分是可以收納一對無綫藍牙耳機，用戶在使用完耳機後，可將耳機套回錶帶內，毋須額外收納盒子，既不容易遺失，也不會忘記攜帶耳機。專利描述續說，耳機除了支援藍牙連接，還兼具抗噪及防水功能，專利更提及一些具體及可行的收納方式，例如隱藏在錶扣、磁力吸附、按扣式等 32 種，十分詳盡。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n分析指 Huawei 對上推出智能手錶產品已是兩年前，如今提交這項設計專利，雖然未知會否實現到第三代 Huawei Watch 3 上，惟外界相信 Huawei 不會單一發展智能手機市場，只是何時會推出新一代自家智能手錶，暫時仍未有任何消息。"},{"pid":"a15c4250c9eefbe2a4f5fc52f1c687bc64bf01df","tid":728770,"uid":183991,"like":0,"dislike":7,"score":-7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-04T04:18:17.000Z","msg":"等睇apple出黎改變世界<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n中國不了"},{"pid":"373653001c76f9358928135d8d4f77dcffe58a33","tid":728770,"uid":36136,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-04T06:22:39.000Z","msg":"佢自家talkband咪重好過依個設計"},{"pid":"7422e31054b89ce35e10aec03d50abbcb7c08db4","tid":728770,"uid":155818,"like":3,"dislike":3,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-04T06:23:36.000Z","msg":"華為真係好比心機係海外市場<br />\n中國都唔覺有咩聲氣"},{"pid":"179bb9ec027f69951cc96530d2971be31f529390","tid":728770,"uid":14737,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-04T06:28:49.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">2025中國製造<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </span></span>"},{"pid":"8c2e71ad324d3bd70ea82718c8d256bb904fd5f5","tid":728770,"uid":183991,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-04T06:42:29.000Z","msg":"除咗apple所有野都係垃圾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"37d2b41cb79b12241a8a1f9f1889985d3be36a86","tid":728770,"uid":51814,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-04T06:44:32.000Z","msg":"又抄邊個設計圖"},{"pid":"a531c9c3e80323c5d0c349960a7a6ba37e560841","tid":728770,"uid":122534,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-04T06:46:29.000Z","msg":"唔係出左好耐咩?<br />\nHUAWEI Talkband B3 Lite"},{"pid":"ec323860e7bb3632ed8aa8917a33b83421e2065e","tid":728770,"uid":43839,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-04T19:31:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bd4f6d171077f0cfc437baafb9f0af1d69f43e27","tid":728770,"uid":80072,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-06T02:00:49.000Z","msg":"出返第一代個樣已經夠啦 攪咁多碌柒嘢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ca553324244dc0833b01f788d0166a229f1e00cf","tid":728770,"uid":174013,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-06T02:05:22.000Z","msg":"即係只係將個耳機